data.description: This well-planned home promotes seamless flow between rooms, encouraging interaction among residents. Privacy is prioritized with the owner's suite separate from other bedrooms, featuring a luxurious bath. Upstairs, three bedrooms with walk-in closets, spacious  game room and two full bathrooms await. The office provides a private workspace, while the gourmet kitchen satisfies discerning chefs. High ceilings and natural light in the family room create a welcoming atmosphere. This impressive 4-bedroom, 3.5-bath home on a cul-de-sac lot offers comfort, luxury, and practicality for family life and entertaining, making it an attractive option for sophisticated living.
